Date: 2024-07-13


VE over time by 1-month interval

  • classify time since vax to testing into three groups: 0-1, 1-2, 2-3, 3-4 and >4 months
  • included confounders: age tested, month tested.
  • uninformative prior for precision of the non-negative increment d’s.
    • d ~ dnorm(0, tau)T(0,)
    • tau_d ~ dgamma(0.01, 0.01)
